    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> tomato paste </strong>to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[7 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tomato base</strong></p>",
